QUICK START
===========

 a) Download and install the required libraries and build tools.

  * J2SE (JRE+JDK) (>= 5.0) <http://java.sun.com/javase/>
  * Stanford Parser (>= 2006-06-11) <http://nlp.stanford.edu/>
  * JSAP (>= 2.1) <http://www.martiansoftware.com/jsap/>
  * MySQL Connector/J (>= 5.0.5) <http://www.mysql.com/products/connector/j/>
  * SAX (>= 2.0) <http://www.saxproject.org/>

  * Apache Ant (recommended) OR Gnu Make

 b) Copy each JAR to /usr/lib/java and modify build.xml or Makefile at
    your own.

 c) Compile and install

   c.1) Using Apache Ant
        $ ant
        $ sudo ant install

   c.2) Using GNU Make
        $ make
        $ sudo make install

 d) Run
